ğŸ‰Stock Buy and Sell â€“ Max 2 Transactions AllowedğŸ†

Approach:
ğŸ‘‰Used a Greedy approach with two variables to track the best buy-sell transactions.
ğŸ‘‰Optimized space complexity by maintaining only four variables.
ğŸ‘‰Time complexity: O(N).

class Solution {
public static int maxProfit(int[] prices) {
        // code here
        int buy1 = Integer.MIN_VALUE, buy2 = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
        int sell1 = 0, sell2 = 0;
       
        for (int price : prices) {
            buy1 = Math.max(buy1, -price);
            sell1 = Math.max(sell1, buy1 + price);
            buy2 = Math.max(buy2, sell1 - price);
            sell2 = Math.max(sell2, buy2 + price);
        }
       
        return sell2;
    }
}